A yearly subscription is refundable within 14 days of purchase and includes a 365-day membership. In a statement on its interim results for the six months ended August 30, 2020 the group said in response to the surge in demand for online shopping during the initial lockdown, Pick n Pay Online launched an on-demand app via partnership with Bottles, “converting it from an online liquor platform into a grocery app in just four days.” It added that Bottles is the highest-rated mobile app in its category, ahead of any other online grocery delivery service in South Africa.